  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  male or female

          -  at least 18 year old

          -  CDI 1st occurrence or 1st recurrence

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  concurrent life threatening condition

          -  concomitant antimicrobial treatment for CDI

          -  concomitant treatment with another investigational drug.
      </textblock>
